#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This guide will introduce you to the many features of the &plasma; workspace "
"and applications and describe many common tasks you can perform."
msgstr ""
"Dit handboek zal u inleiden in de vele functies van &plasma;-workspace en "
"applications, en vele gemeenschappelijke taken beschrijven die u kunt "
"uitvoeren."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
