"For more information on &kde;, visit the <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/"
"\">KDE website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Voor meer informatie over &kde;, zie de <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/"
"\">KDE website</ulink>."

